### ── Codelab 04 — Arquitectura limpia y excepciones ─────────────────

### 1. GET CPU existente -> 200 OK con body
GET http://localhost:8082/api/v1/component-service/cpus/1
Accept: application/json

###

### 2. GET CPU inexistente -> 404 con ApiErrorResponse JSON
GET http://localhost:8082/api/v1/component-service/cpus/999
Accept: application/json

###

### 3. PUT CPU existente -> 200 OK
PUT http://localhost:8082/api/v1/component-service/cpus/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
	"brand": "AMD",
	"model": "Ryzen 9 9900X",
	"socket": "AM5",
	"cores": 12,
	"threads": 24,
	"tdp": 170,
	"price": 2399000
}

###

### 4. PUT CPU inexistente -> 404 con ApiErrorResponse JSON
PUT http://localhost:8082/api/v1/component-service/cpus/999
Content-Type: application/json

{
	"brand": "Fantasma",
	"model": "Digital",
	"socket": "AM5",
	"cores": 8,
	"threads": 16,
	"tdp": 105,
	"price": 1899000
}

###

### 5. DELETE CPU existente -> 204 No Content
DELETE http://localhost:8082/api/v1/component-service/cpus/1
Accept: application/json

###

### 6. DELETE CPU inexistente -> 404 con ApiErrorResponse JSON
DELETE http://localhost:8082/api/v1/component-service/cpus/999
Accept: application/json

###

### 7. POST inválido -> 400 con mapa de errores por campo
POST http://localhost:8082/api/v1/component-service/rams
Content-Type: application/json

{
	"brand": "",
	"model": "",
	"type": "DDR5",
	"capacity": 32,
	"speed": 6000,
	"price": -100
}

###

### 8. POST válido -> 201 Created
POST http://localhost:8082/api/v1/component-service/rams
Content-Type: application/json

{
	"brand": "Corsair",
	"model": "Vengeance RGB",
	"type": "DDR5",
	"capacity": 32,
	"speed": 6000,
	"price": 850000
}

###

### 9. Listar paginado -> página 0, 4 elementos
GET http://localhost:8082/api/v1/component-service/cpus
Accept: application/json

###

### 10. Health check con estado de la BD
GET http://localhost:8082/actuator/health
Accept: application/json

###
